<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE reference PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Reference//EN" "technicalContent/dtd/reference.dtd">
<reference id="mediaplayeritemloader-loaderlistener"
 xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/"> 
  <title>Loader events</title> 
  <shortdesc><ph conkeyref="phrases/primetime-sdk-name"/> dispatches media
	 player item events in response to loading a media item. 
  </shortdesc> 
  <refbody> 
	 <refsyn> 
		<p>These events provide an alternative workflow. You are not required to implement this interface
				when creating a <codeph>MediaPlayer</codeph>. Use this when you want to have a
					<codeph>MediaPlayerItemLoader</codeph>.</p> 
		<p>To be notified about events related to loading a media player resource, register listeners for
				the following events with the <codeph>MediaPlayerItemLoader</codeph> object.</p> 
		<table frame="all" colsep="1" rowsep="1"> 
		  <tgroup cols="2" colsep="1" rowsep="1" outputclass="FormatA"> 
			 <colspec colnum="1" colname="1" colwidth="41*"/> 
			 <colspec colnum="2" colname="2" colwidth="59*"/> 
			 <thead> 
				<row rowsep="1"> 
				  <entry colname="1">Event 
				  </entry> 
				  <entry colname="2">Meaning 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
			 </thead> 
			 <tbody> 
				<row rowsep="1" > 
				  <entry colname="1"><codeph>MediaPlayerItemLoader.<xref
										href="http://help.adobe.com/en_US/primetime/api/psdk/asdoc-dhls_1.4/com/adobe/mediacore/MediaPlayerItemLoader.html#event:completed"
										format="html" scope="external"
								>completed</xref></codeph></entry> 
				  <entry colname="2">Media resource loading completed successfully.
					 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
				<row rowsep="1" > 
				  <entry colname="1"><codeph>MediaPlayerItemLoader.<xref
										href="http://help.adobe.com/en_US/primetime/api/psdk/asdoc-dhls_1.4/com/adobe/mediacore/MediaPlayerItemLoader.html#event:failed"
										format="html" scope="external"
								>failed</xref></codeph></entry> 
				  <entry colname="2">A problem occurred with media resource
					 loading. 
				  </entry> 
				</row> 
			 </tbody> 
		  </tgroup> 
		</table> 
	 </refsyn> 
  </refbody> 
</reference> 
